<text id="02-output-contract" title="RACI AI Assisted Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for `RACIMatrix` — exactly one accountable per row, evidence-anchored assignments, named owner, last_reviewed within window.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/raci-matrix.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["project_id", "header", "rows", "review_log"],
  "properties": {
    "project_id": {"type": "string"},
    "header": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["owner", "last_reviewed", "version", "trigger"],
      "properties": {
        "owner": {"type": "object", "required": ["role", "person"], "properties": {"role": {"type": "string"}, "person": {"type": "string", "minLength": 2}}},
        "last_reviewed": {"type": "string", "format": "date"},
        "version": {"type": "string"},
        "trigger": {"enum": ["kickoff", "roster_delta", "quarterly_review"]}
      }
    },
    "rows": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["wbs_id", "deliverable", "responsible", "accountable", "consulted", "informed", "evidence"],
        "properties": {
          "wbs_id": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[0-9]+(\\.[0-9]+)*$"},
          "deliverable": {"type": "string"},
          "responsible": {"type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": {"type": "string"}},
          "accountable": {"type": "string", "minLength": 2},
          "consulted": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}},
          "informed": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}},
          "evidence": {"type": "array", "minItems": 1, "items": {"type": "string"}}
        }
      }
    },
    "review_log": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "required": ["reviewed_at"]}}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>`accountable` empty or matching `^team|tbd|various$` — violates `r4-named-owner`.</item>
      <item>Two rows naming the same role as `accountable` for the same WBS branch (duplicate A) — violates RACI invariant.</item>
      <item>`responsible` empty for a non-trivial leaf — orphaned R.</item>
      <item>`evidence` empty — violates `r3-evidence-anchored`.</item>
      <item>`header.trigger` value outside enum — violates `r1-explicit-trigger`.</item>
      <item>`header.last_reviewed` &gt; 90 days — violates `r5-iteration-loop`.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "project_id": "checkout",
  "header": {"owner": {"role": "PM", "person": "pm-handle"}, "last_reviewed": "2026-05-10", "version": "1.4", "trigger": "roster_delta"},
  "rows": [
    {"wbs_id": "2.1", "deliverable": "Login Endpoint", "responsible": ["backend-engineer"], "accountable": "backend-lead",
     "consulted": ["security-lead"], "informed": ["PM"], "evidence": ["charter#auth-section", "wbs-dict#2.1"]}
  ],
  "review_log": [{"reviewed_at": "2026-05-10"}]
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "project_id": "x",
  "header": {"owner": {"role": "team", "person": ""}, "last_reviewed": "2024-01-01", "version": "0", "trigger": "when_needed"},
  "rows": [
    {"wbs_id": "2.1", "deliverable": "Login", "responsible": [], "accountable": "", "consulted": [], "informed": [], "evidence": []}
  ],
  "review_log": []
}
]]></code>
    <note>owner.person empty; trigger invalid; last_reviewed stale; row has empty responsible/accountable/evidence.</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-raci-ai-assisted.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
